results.name: a(n) = 2*A194695(n).
comment: Conjecture: number of toothpicks or D-toothpicks added to the structure of A194442 at stage 2^k+n, if k tends to infinity. It appears that rows of A194443 when written as a triangle converge to this sequence.
link: N. J. A. Sloane, Catalog of Toothpick and Cellular Automata Sequences in the OEIS
